- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper focuses on translating CUDA programs to OpenCL programs. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses a neural machine translation model. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper discusses pre/post processing steps for program translation. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions using benchmarks for testing the translation model.
